{"id": "jos028", "name": "Cam_Cafe_702_10_01", "res": "jos2801.mp4", "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Door_Bell", "Doorbell"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Hello, sit anywhere you like.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Do you have saké?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Yep, wait one sec.\nDo you want it heated?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "No.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Never seen you before. Are you from the east? Node 03?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Yes. Is it rare to see one around these places?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Nah, where do you think this is? It's 08, any type of people can be found here.\nBut cold saké... indeed not an order you see every day.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Back home we call this \"Yukihie\", refreshes the brain quite well... <i>*Gulp!*</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Yukihie, I see...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<i>*Gulp!*</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Jasus, slow down. If you get drunk so fast, I'm gonna be the one carrying your limp body outside.\nI've always had a fond interest in chatting with customers from other Nodes.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "I'm... not exactly the type who's good at chatting.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Haha, it's fine. I'm JOE, and you are?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Hayato... <i>*Gulp!*</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Did you get dumped?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "... Why did you ask?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Well, a young fella with a depressed look visiting an unfamiliar bar with the sole purpose of getting trashed. Pretty sure that means it has something to do with relationship issues... I think?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "I'm... looking for a female.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Girlfriend?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "More or less my childhood friend, been missing for years already... <i>*Gulp!*</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "For years... could it be that she already... ah, I'm sorry.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "No need to be...I gave up a long time ago too. In Node 03, missing people usually stay missing forever. It's practically a part of everyday life.\nHowever, for some unknown reason, I just always have this feeling that she is right here in Node 08. A very powerful feeling too...<i>*Gulp!*</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... If you're looking for someone, maybe you've come to the right location.\nNot to brag about it, but this little shop really has all kinds of people visiting every day. Give me some hints, maybe I can help. If you have a photo, even better.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "A photo... I always have it with me. Here.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Hoho, lemme take a look. Heard from folks that Node 03 is where all the cute gals are at...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "...... This person......\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "...... zzZ......\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... He's drunk.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...... Kaori......</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Door_Bell", "ドアベル"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "いらっしゃい。お好きなところにどうぞ。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "日本酒はありますか？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "日本酒ね。\n温める？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "いえ。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "お客さん、見たことない顔だね。\n東方の人？Node03出身？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "はい、ここにはあまりいないんですか？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "まさか。\nNode08にはどんな人間だっているよ。\nでも、冷たい日本酒を頼む人は珍しいね。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "僕の故郷では、「雪冷え」って言います。\n飲むと頭がシャキッとするんですよ。\nゴクッ\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "「雪冷え」…か……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "ゴクッ\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "ちょっと、お客さんペース速すぎ！\n酔っぱらっちゃったら、追い出さないといけなくなっちゃうから。\n俺、他のNodeの人と話すの好きなんだよ。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "僕は…話すのとか得意じゃないです。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "ハハハ！大丈夫だって！\n俺はJOE、君は？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "隼人……\nゴク\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "何？失恋？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……なんでですか？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "夜中に一人で、入ったことのないバーで、浴びるように酒を飲む若者なんて、80％落ち込んだ人間だよ。……タブン。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "女の人を……探してるんです。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "彼女？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "幼なじみで、もう何年も前に行方不明になっちゃったんですけど……\nゴクッ\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "何年も前……それじゃ、もしかすると……あっ、ご、ごめん。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "いえ…僕も半ば諦めかけてたんです。\nNode03では、人が消えて二度と帰って来ないなんて日常茶飯事ですから。\nでも、なんか、彼女はNode08にいるような気がして。\nそれもなぜだか強烈にそう感じるんです……\nゴクッ\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……人探しなら、ここに来たのは正解かもね。\n自慢じゃないけど、ここには本当にどんな人間でもいるから。\n手掛かりさえあれば、手伝えるかもしれない。\n写真とかないの？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "写真……ずっと持ち歩いてます。\nこれ……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "お、どれどれ。\nいやぁ、Node03は美女ばかりって聞くからなぁ……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……この子は……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……zzZ……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "…寝ちゃったか。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……カオリ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Door_Bell", "門鈴"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你好，隨便坐啊。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "有清酒嗎？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "有啊，稍等。\n要加熱嗎？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "不用了。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "沒見過你耶，東方人？Node 03 來的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "嗯，這邊很少見嗎？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "怎麼可能，這邊是 08 耶，什麼人都有。\n點冰清酒的人就真的很少了。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "這在我們那叫「雪冷」，很醒腦……<i>*咕！*</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "「雪冷」啊……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<i>*咕！*</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "喂，喝慢點吧，你要是一下就醉了我要負責趕你出去耶。\n我一直很喜歡跟其他 Node 的客人聊天的。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "我……不是很會聊天的那種人。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈哈，沒關係。我叫JOE，你呢？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Hayato……<i>*咕！*</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你是失戀了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……為什麼這麼問？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "半夜一個人跑到沒去過的酒吧狂灌酒、一臉憂鬱的年輕人，八成是遇到什麼感情上的問題……吧？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "我在……找一個女的。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "女朋友？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "算青梅竹馬吧，已經失蹤好幾年了……<i>*咕！*</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "好幾年……會不會已經……啊，抱歉。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "不……其實我也很早之前就放棄了，我們都住在 Node 03，人口失蹤找不回來是很平常的事情。\n但是我不知道為什麼一直有她就在 Node 08 的感覺，而且很強烈……<i>*咕！*</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……要找人的話，也許你來對地方了。\n不是我要自誇，這間店真的各式各樣的人都有，你給一些線索，也許我能幫上忙，如果有照片就更好了。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "照片……我隨身都帶著，這裡。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "喔喔，我看看，聽說 Node 03 專出正妹呢……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……這個人……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……zzZ……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……醉倒了。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……Kaori……</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Door_Bell", "도어벨"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "어서오세요. 아무데나 앉으세요~\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "혹시 사케도 있습니까?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "네~ 잠시만요.\n데워드릴까요?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "괜찮습니다.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "한 번도 본적이 없는데... 동양인? Node 03에서 오셨나요?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "네. 여기선 마주치기 힘들죠?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "그럴리가~\n이곳은 Node 08! 별의 별 사람들이 다 모여있죠. 물론 차가운 사케를 주문하는 사람은 거의 없었지만 말이죠.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "우리 고향에선 「유키히에」라고 부른답니다. \n머리가 아주 맑아지죠.... *꿀꺽*\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "「유키히에」라……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<i>*꿀꺽*</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "저기, 손님! 너무 빨리 마시는 것 같은데? \n여기서 완전히 취해버리면 제가 또 부축해야 한다고요!\n얘기도 좀 나누면서 좀 천천히, 오케이?\n전 다른 Node 출신 손님이랑 얘길 나누는 것을 굉장히 좋아하거든요\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "전…… 그렇게 얘기를 잘 하는 사람이 아닙니다만.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "하하하! 괜찮아요! 내 이름은 JOE. 당신은?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Hayato……*꿀꺽*\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "실연이라도 당했나봐요?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……왜 그렇게 묻는 거죠?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "우울한 표정을 한 젊은 사람이 새벽에 혼자 한 번도 가본 적이 없는 술집에 들어가 술을 들이 붓는다! \n그럼 딱 80% 이상은 내가 추측한 것이 맞다....고 생각이 드는데?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "어떤 여자를…… 찾고 있어요.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "여자친구?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "소꿉친구죠. 이미 실종된지 몇 년이나 지났지만......*꿀꺽*\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "몇 년이라……그럼 이미……아, 죄송합니다.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "아니요…… 사실 저도 일찍이 포기했어요. 저희 둘 다 Node 03 출신이었으니. 그곳에선 사람이 실종되고 행방이 묘연해지는 일은 일상다반사였죠.\n이유는 모르겠지만 계속 그녀가 Node 08에 있을 거라는 예감이 강하게 들어서.....*꿀꺽*\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……사람을 찾는 거라면, 아마 장소를 제대로 짚으신 것 같군.\n과장이 아니라, 이 곳엔 별의별 사람들이 다 모인다고 했죠?\n아마 조금이라도 단서를 준다면, 아마 제가 도울 수 있을지도 몰라요. 사진 같은 게 있으면 더욱 수월할 테고!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "사진……항상 몸에 지니고 다니죠. 자, 여기.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "오오! 어디 한번!\n듣기론 Node 03에 미인이 그렇게 많다던데....\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……이 사람은……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……zzZ……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……취해서 잠들어버렸군.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……Kaori……</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Door_Bell", "門鈴"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你好，隨便坐啊。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "有清酒嗎？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "有啊，稍等。\n要加熱嗎？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "不用了。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "沒見過你耶，東方人？Node 03 來的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "嗯，這邊很少見嗎？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "怎麼可能，這邊是 08 耶，什麼人都有。\n點冰清酒的人就真的很少了。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "這在我們那叫「雪冷」，很醒腦……<i>*咕！*</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "「雪冷」啊……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<i>*咕！*</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "喂，喝慢點吧，你要是一下就醉了我要負責趕你出去耶。\n我一直很喜歡跟其他 Node 的客人聊天的。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "我……不是很會聊天的那種人。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈哈，沒關係。我叫JOE，你呢？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Hayato……<i>*咕！*</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你是失戀了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……為什麼這麼問？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "半夜一個人跑到沒去過的酒吧狂灌酒、一臉憂鬱的年輕人，八成是遇到什麼感情上的問題……吧？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "我在……找一個女的。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "女朋友？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "算青梅竹馬吧，已經失蹤好幾年了……<i>*咕！*</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "好幾年……會不會已經……啊，抱歉。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "不……其實我也很早之前就放棄了，我們都住在 Node 03，人口失蹤找不回來是很平常的事情。\n但是我不知道為什麼一直有她就在 Node 08 的感覺，而且很強烈……<i>*咕！*</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……要找人的話，也許你來對地方了。\n不是我要自誇，這間店真的各式各樣的人都有，你給一些線索，也許我能幫上忙，如果有照片就更好了。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "照片……我隨身都帶著，這裡。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "喔喔，我看看，聽說 Node 03 專出正妹呢……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……這個人……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……zzZ……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……醉倒了。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……Kaori……</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Door_Bell", "门铃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你好，随便坐啊。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "有清酒吗？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "有啊，稍等。\n要加热吗？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "不用了。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "没见过你耶，东方人？ Node 03 来的吗？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "嗯，这边很少见吗？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "怎么可能，这边是 08 耶，什么人都有。\n点冰清酒的人就真的很少了。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "这在我们那叫「雪冷」，很醒脑……<i>*咕！ *</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "「雪冷」啊……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<i>*咕！ *</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversati